# Interface Layer - Copilot Instructions

## Propósito
La capa de interfaz expone los servicios de la aplicación como endpoints HTTP REST.

## Estructura
- **controllers.py**: Endpoints y routers
- Organizar por dominios (auth_router, user_router, product_router, etc.)

## Responsabilidades
- Definir endpoints REST
- Validar requests con DTOs
- Transformar responses
- Documentar en Swagger
- Gestionar autenticación

## Patrones de Endpoints

### GET - Obtener
```python
@router.get(
    "/{id}",
    response_model=EntityResponse,
    summary="Obtener entidad",
    description="Obtiene una entidad por ID"
)
async def get_entity(
    id: int,
    db: Session = Depends(get_db),
    current_user: dict = Depends(get_current_user)
) -> EntityResponse:
    service = EntityService(db)
    return service.get(id)
```

### POST - Crear
```python
@router.post(
    "",
    response_model=EntityResponse,
    status_code=status.HTTP_201_CREATED,
    summary="Crear entidad",
    description="Crea una nueva entidad"
)
async def create_entity(
    entity_create: EntityCreate,
    db: Session = Depends(get_db),
    current_user: dict = Depends(get_current_user)
) -> EntityResponse:
    service = EntityService(db)
    return service.create(entity_create)
```

### PUT - Actualizar
```python
@router.put(
    "/{id}",
    response_model=EntityResponse,
    summary="Actualizar entidad"
)
async def update_entity(
    id: int,
    entity_update: EntityUpdate,
    db: Session = Depends(get_db),
    current_user: dict = Depends(get_current_user)
) -> EntityResponse:
    service = EntityService(db)
    return service.update(id, entity_update)
```

### DELETE - Eliminar
```python
@router.delete(
    "/{id}",
    status_code=status.HTTP_204_NO_CONTENT,
    summary="Eliminar entidad"
)
async def delete_entity(
    id: int,
    db: Session = Depends(get_db),
    current_user: dict = Depends(get_current_user)
):
    service = EntityService(db)
    if not service.delete(id):
        raise HTTPException(status_code=404, detail="Not found")
```

## Documentación Swagger

### Minimal
